font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>COPD-i&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351; &ccedil;&auml;releri &ccedil;ilim &ccedil;ekmek,
i&#351; &yacute;erlerine t&auml;sir etmek we i&ccedil;erde we da&#351;arda
hapalanmak &yacute;aly t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik faktorlaryny &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarmagy,
azaltmagy we dolandyrmagy &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar.&nbsp;COPD
hassalaryna COPD-i&#328; g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmegini&#328;
t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;iligini azald&yacute;an d&uuml;mewden we bu hassalarda
pnewmokokk pnewmoni&yacute;asyny&#328; d&ouml;remegini ep-esli azald&yacute;an
pnewmokokk &yacute;okan&ccedil;lygyna gar&#351;y sanjym edilmegi maslahat
